::Feline::

She lookd at the two bots. She transformed into leapord mode and 
jumped up on the counter top.  She layed down and started to groom 
herself.  She licked her paws.  She glided her long tongue up her arm 
from her elbow in slow, even strokes.  She licked the top side, then 
the sides of her arm.  She looked up at the two and purred.
